definitions.definition: Lacking proprietary value; not private or privileged information; not owned by anyone (not anyone's property , whether intellectual property or otherwise).

subdefinitions.definition: Not protected by trademark, patent, or trade secret and thus open to commercial use without license; said of drugs (medications) and of various kinds of goods and materials.

main_definition: Lacking proprietary value; not private or privileged information; not owned by anyone (not anyone's property , whether intellectual property or otherwise).
